                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18430821-2589-offence-1 t18430821-cd-315"></join>16th of Aug</rs>., I bonnet, value 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; 6 yards of ribbon, 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 2 pairs of gloves, 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., 3/4 of a yard of lawn, 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; 1 pocket handkerchief, 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; and 3 artificial flowers, 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18430821-name-1864" type="victimName">
